    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "\n*Followup to https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/30889*\n\n### Problem\n\n`vim.ui.img` does not have a healthcheck\n\n### Expected behavior\n\n- use `TermResponse` (`runtime/lua/vim/tty.lua`) to detect if the host-terminal supports kitty graphics protocol.\n    - show a meaningful error if `vim.ui.img` is called but we know the host-terminal doesn't support images.\n- update the Terminal section of `runtime/lua/vim/health/health.lua` to report whether images are supported",
    "closed_at": "2026-04-28T14:12:15Z",
    "closed_by": {
        "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1359421?v=4",
        "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/justinmk/events{/privacy}",
